\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces \textbf  {Pareto-optimal drug target combinations} identified from the potency-toxicity landscape. All combinations involve accA (fatty acid synthesis) paired with LPS-related pathway targets. The identical potency/toxicity/quality values across all six combinations reflect the fact that both accA and all LPS targets are individually lethal in FBA, yielding the same double-knockout phenotype. Differentiation among these combinations would require experimental synergy assays at sub-inhibitory concentrations.}}{16}{table.2}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{tab:pareto}{{2}{16}{\textbf {Pareto-optimal drug target combinations} identified from the potency-toxicity landscape. All combinations involve accA (fatty acid synthesis) paired with LPS-related pathway targets. The identical potency/toxicity/quality values across all six combinations reflect the fact that both accA and all LPS targets are individually lethal in FBA, yielding the same double-knockout phenotype. Differentiation among these combinations would require experimental synergy assays at sub-inhibitory concentrations}{table.2}{}}
